metadata.name: Gothic Santa Pepe
metadata.description:
Hand drawn original digital painting of Pepe created in my author’s style and inspired by a dark gothic aesthetic that is a main theme of my art. No photoshop or any other editing used.

Santa Pepe is a symbol of the Strength and the Steadfastness of one’s Uniqueness in a heavy and unpredictable flow of trends, fashion or relevances.

She’s calm, wise and confident. No change of fashion bothers her. She knows that time flies, interests change, new trends appear and die. But she stays gorgeous in her own way, she’s out of the time and space.
Nothing will ever shake her identity and independence.
